y\">Necromancy Talent</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/necromancer/#undead-body\">Undead Body</a>&nbsp;(DR 2),&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/necromancer/#secrets-of-the-dead\">Secrets of the Dead</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>7th</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/necromancer/#life-sight\">Life Sight</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/necromancer/#cheat-death\">Cheat Death</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/necromancer/#harm-touch\">Harm Touch</a>&nbsp;(3d6)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>8th</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/necromancer/#undead-body\">Necromancy Talent</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/necromancer/#unlife-healer\">Unlife Healer</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>9th</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/necromancer/#miasma\">Miasma</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/necromancer/#harm-touch\">Harm Touch</a>&nbsp;(4d6)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>10th</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/necromancer/#clear-mind\">Clear Mind</a>&nbsp;II,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/necromancer/#undead-body\">Necromancy Talent</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/necromancer/#undead-body\">Undead Body</a>&nbsp;(DR 3),&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/necromancer/#fortification\">Unholy Protection</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>11th</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/necromancer/#undead-mastery\">Undead Mastery</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/necromancer/#harm-touch\">Harm Touch</a>&nbsp;(5d6)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>12th</td>\n<td><a href=