{"_id":"IypiHIcEW9wFT0oO","name":"Bone Minion - HD","type":"class","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Make sure this classe's level follows the chart below for HD.</p>\n<h2 id=\"tablepress-50-name\">Table: Bone Minion</h2>\n<table id=\"tablepress-50\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"5\" aria-labelledby=\"tablepress-50-name\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>\n<p>Necromancer</p>\n<p>Class Level</p>\n</th>\n<th>HD</th>\n<th>Special</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>3rd</td>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>Undead traits, link</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4th</td>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>&mdash;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5th</td>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>&mdash;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>6th</td>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>&mdash;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>7th</td>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>&mdash;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>8th</td>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>&mdash;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>9th</td>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>&mdash;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>10th</td>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>&mdash;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>11th</td>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>&mdash;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>12th</td>\n<td>6</td>\n<td>&mdash;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>13th</td>\n<td>6</td>\n<td>&mdash;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>14th</td>\n<td>7</td>\n<td>&mdash;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>15th</td>\n<td>7</td>\n<td>&mdash;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>16th</td>\n<td>8</td>\n<td>&mdash;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>17th</td>\n<td>8</td>\n<td>&mdash;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>18th</td>\n<td>9</td>\n<td>&mdash;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>19th</td>\n<td>9</td>\n<td>&mdash;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>20th</td>\n<td>10</td>\n<td>&mdash;</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>Class Level:&nbsp;The character&rsquo;s necromancer level. The necromancer&rsquo;s class levels stack with levels of any other classes that are entitled to a bone minion for the purpose of determining the bone minion&rsquo;s statistics.</p>\n<p>HD:&nbsp;This is the total number of eight-<wbr />sided (d8) Hit Dice the bone minion possesses, but it possesses no Constitution score. Bone minions use their Charisma score in place of their Constitution score.</p>\n<p>BAB:&nbsp;This is the bone minion&rsquo;s base attack bonus. Bone minions do not gain additional attacks using their natural weapons for a high base attack bonus.</p>\n<p>Fort/Ref/Will:&nbsp;These are the bone minion&rsquo;s base saving throw bonuses. Bone minions have good Will saves.</p>\n<p>Undead Traits (Ex):&nbsp;Bone minions have darkvision out to a range of 60 feet, have immunity to poison, sleep, disable, immobilize and stunning status effects. Immunity to any effect that requires a Fortitude save (unless the effect also works on objects or is harmless). Not at risk of death from massive damage, but are immediately destroyed when reduced to 0 hit points. Not affected by&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/magic/spells/r/raise/\">Raise</a>&nbsp;spells or abilities. Absorbs any shadow damage, and takes half again as much from holy damage.</p>\n<p>Link (Ex): A bone commander and its bone minions share a mental link allows for communication across any distance (as long as they are on the same plane). If the bone commander is destroyed, the bone minions are destroyed as well.</p>","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"links":{"children":[],"classAssociations":[{"name":"Undead Traits - Bone Minion","level":1,"uuid":"Compendium.ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-base_necromancer.K1OQ5dQoa6I8CjAi"},{"name":"Link - Bone Minion","level":1,"uuid":"Compendium.ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-base_necromancer.DNoTZolkDqJr94im"}]},"tag":"boneCommanderHd","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{"boolean":{},"dictionary":{}},"scriptCalls":[],"subType":"racial","classSubType":"none","parentClass":"Necromancer","level":1,"lvl":0,"countforexp":"exp","hd":8,"hp":8,"classCastingStat":"noncaster","classBaseMPTypes":"noncaster","classBaseMPauto":"yes","mp":0,"bab":"med","skillsPerLevel":0,"savingThrows":{"fort":{"value":"low"},"ref":{"value":"low"},"will":{"value":"high"}},"fc":{"hp":{"value":0},"skill":{"value":0},"alt":{"value":0,"notes":""}},"classSkills":{"acr":false,"apr":false,"blf":false,"clm":false,"crf":false,"dip":false,"dev":false,"dis":false,"dri":false,"esc":false,"fly":false,"han":false,"hea":false,"int":false,"kar":false,"kdu":false,"ken":false,"kge":false,"khi":false,"klo":false,"kna":false,"kno":false,"kpl":false,"kre":false,"kte":false,"lin":false,"nav":false,"per":false,"prf":false,"pil":false,"pro":false,"rep":false,"rid":false,"sen":false,"slt":false,"spl":false,"ste":false,"sur":false,"swm":false,"umd":false},"levels":{"value":0,"_deprecated":true},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0}},"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"systemId":"ffd20","systemVersion":"10.2.4","coreVersion":"10.303","createdTime":1667698089394,"modifiedTime":1694209595641,"lastModifiedBy":"VNk1dF8h7rdEhEd4"},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_yib1f2jjgvh"}}}
