{"_id":"PSzzikWkTlSf6FVz","name":"Necromancy Talents","type":"feat","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"description":{"value":"<p class=\"western\">As a necromancer gains experience, he learns a number of talents that assist him in manipulating undead and empower his necromancy. At 2nd level and every two levels thereafter, a necromancer gains one necromancy talent. A necromancer cannot select an individual talent more than once. Talents marked with an asterisk add effects to a necromancer&rsquo;s spellcasting ability. Only one of these talents can be applied to an individual spell and the decision must be made before the spell is cast.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li>A complete list of necromancy talents can be found here: <a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/necromancer/necromancy-talents/\">Necromancy Talents</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"western\">At 12th a necromancer learns further talents to assist him in manipulating undead and mastering necromancy. He may choose one of the following advanced necromancy talents in place of a necromancy talent. Talents marked with an asterisk add effects to a necromancer&rsquo;s spellcasting ability. Only one of these talents can be applied to an individual spell and the decision must be made before the spell is cast.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li>A complete list of advanced necromancy talents can be found here: <a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/necromancer/necromancy-talents/\">Advanced Necromancy Talents</a></li>\n</ul>","unidentified":""},"tags":["Necromancy Talent","Advanced Necromancy Talents"],"actions":[],"uses":{"per":null,"value":0,"maxFormula":"","autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"attackNotes":[],"effectNotes":[],"changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{"boolean":{},"dictionary":{}},"scriptCalls":[],"subType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":["Necromancer"]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","disabled":false,"classSkills":{},"ability":{"damageMult":1,"critMult":2}},"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"systemId":"ffd20","systemVersion":"10.2.4","coreVersion":"10.303","createdTime":1667698089408,"modifiedTime":1694209595641,"lastModifiedBy":"VNk1dF8h7rdEhEd4"},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_mlzefn8ai9d"}}}
{"_id":"R103szBRYqNNH3MU","name":"Bone Minion - Abilities - Archer","type":"class","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>These bone minions uses bows to fire arrows from ranged. They begin play with Light Armor proficiency,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/feats/combat-feats/precise-shot-combat-final/\">Precise Shot</a>, and are proficient with all bows. When the necromancer reaches 11th level, bone archers receive the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/feats/combat-feats/rapid-shot-combat-final/\">Rapid Shot</a>&nbsp;feat. At 17th level, bone warriors receive the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/feats/combat-feats/manyshot-combat-final/\">Manyshot</a>&nbsp;feat. These bone archers are summoned with a +1 long bow and light armor which increases to +2 at 11th level, and +3 at 17th level. The bone archers have an unlimited supply of arrows. These items disappear when the bone archer is destroyed or removed from the bone archer&rsquo;s possession.</p>","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"links":{"children":[],"classAssociations":[{"name":"Precise Shot","level":1,"uuid":"Compendium.ffd20.feats.53urYIbYYpQuoSLd"},{"name":"Rapid Shot","level":11,"uuid":"Compendium.ffd20.feats.NABgOSBRECIREaha"},{"name":"Manyshot","level":17,"uuid":"Compendium.ffd20.feats.w23dO02t0poRrno0"}]},"tag":"boneCommanderHd","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":["lgt"],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":"All Bows"},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{"boolean":{},"dictionary":{}},"scriptCalls":[],"subType":"racial","classSubType":"none","parentClass":"Necromancer","level":1,"lvl":0,"countforexp":"noExp","hd":0,"hp":0,"classCastingStat":"noncaster","classBaseMPTypes":"noncaster","classBaseMPauto":"yes","mp":0,"bab":"","skillsPerLevel":0,"savingThrows":{"fort":{"value":""},"ref":{"value":""},"will":{"value