{"_id":"fOWCJrxhvHgrHUwT","name":"Bone Minion - Abilities - Mender","type":"class","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>These bone minions cast cure spells. They begin play with Power Staff proficiency,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/magic/spells/c/cure/\">cure</a>&nbsp;spell and use the necromancer&rsquo;s MP pool to cast. When the necromancer reaches 11th level, bone menders can cast&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/magic/spells/c/cure-ii/\">cure II&nbsp;</a>spell. At 17th level, bone menders can cast&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/magic/spells/c/cure-iii/\">cure III</a>&nbsp;spell. Bone menders use their own level as their spell-<wbr />casting level, but utilizes the necromancer&rsquo;s Charisma modifier as their casting attribute. These bone menders are summoned with a +1 dark power staff which increases to +2 at 11th level, and +3 at 17th level. This item disappears when the bone mender is destroyed or removed from the bone mender&rsquo;s possession.</p>","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"links":{"children":[],"classAssociations":[]},"tag":"boneCommanderHd","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":"Power Staff"},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{"boolean":{},"dictionary":{}},"scriptCalls":[],"subType":"racial","classSubType":"none","parentClass":"Necromancer","level":1,"lvl":0,"countforexp":"noExp","hd":0,"hp":0,"classCastingStat":"noncaster","classBaseMPTypes":"noncaster","classBaseMPauto":"yes","mp":0,"bab":"","skillsPerLevel":0,"savingThrows":{"fort":{"value":""},"ref":{"value":""},"will":{"value":""}},"fc":{"hp":{"value":0},"skill":{"value":0},"alt":{"value":0,"notes":""}},"classSkills":{"acr":false,"apr":false,"blf":false,"clm":false,"crf":false,"dip":false,"dev":false,"dis":false,"dri":false,"esc