{"_id":"jIYOYqNYWBJPdXvq","name":"Bone Minion - Abilities - Fighter","type":"class","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>These bone minions are front-<wbr />line melee. They begin play with Light and Medium Armor proficiency,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/feats/combat-feats/weapon-focus-combat-final/\">Weapon Focus</a>&nbsp;(weapon chosen by necromancer), and are proficient with all simple and martial weapons. When the necromancer reaches 11th level, bone fighters receive the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/feats/combat-feats/power-attack-combat-final/\">Power Attack</a>&nbsp;feat. At 17th level, bone fighters receive the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/feats/combat-feats/weapon-specialization-combat-final/\">Weapon Specialization</a>&nbsp;feat (weapon chosen from Weapon Focus feat). These bone fighters are summoned with a +1 weapon and armor which increases to +2 at 11th level, and +3 at 17th level. These items disappear when the bone fighter are destroyed or removed from the bone fighter&rsquo;s possession.</p>","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"links":{"children":[],"classAssociations":[{"name":"Weapon Focus","level":1,"uuid":"Compendium.ffd20.feats.n250dFlbykAIAg5Z"},{"name":"Power Attack","level":11,"uuid":"Compendium.ffd20.feats.FUW5mIXHNBBIQ1Sq"},{"name":"Weapon Specialization","level":17,"uuid":"Compendium.ffd20.feats.YLCvMNeAF9V31m1h"}]},"tag":"boneCommanderHd","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":["lgt","med"],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":["sim","mar"],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{"boolean":{},"dictionary":{}},"scriptCalls":[],"subType":"racial","classSubType":"none","parentClass":"Necromancer","level":1,"lvl":0,"countforexp":"noExp","hd":0,"hp":0,"classCastingStat":"noncaster","classBaseMPTypes":"noncaster","classBaseMPauto":"yes","mp":0